# Permissions & Game Rules

Authoritative permission matrices, ownership edge cases, and GUI enablement rules: [.github/instructions/game-rules.instructions.md](../../.github/instructions/game-rules.instructions.md).

- **Ownership:** Creator-based; persisted via `chart_tag.last_user`.
- **Checks:** Use `AdminUtils` for permission logic. Admins override.
- **Audit:** Log admin overrides with `AdminUtils.log_admin_action`.
- **Visuals:** Disable (do not hide) disallowed actions; use explanatory tooltips.
